{"tha-ap533:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap533:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap533:0.3":"1 Mahakaccayanattheraapadana ","tha-ap533:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap533:1.2":"anejo ajitam jayo; ","tha-ap533:1.3":"Satasahasse kappanam, ","tha-ap533:1.4":"ito uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap533:2.1":"Viro kamalapattakkho, ","tha-ap533:2.2":"sasankavimalanano; ","tha-ap533:2.3":"Kanakacalasankaso, ","tha-ap533:2.4":"ravidittisamappabho. ","tha-ap533:3.1":"Sattanettamanohari, ","tha-ap533:3.2":"varalakkhanabhusito; ","tha-ap533:3.3":"Sabbavakyapathatito, ","tha-ap533:3.4":"manujamarasakkato. ","tha-ap533:4.1":"Sambuddho bodhayam satte, ","tha-ap533:4.2":"vagiso madhurassaro; ","tha-ap533:4.3":"Karunanibandhasantano, ","tha-ap533:4.4":"parisasu visarado. ","tha-ap533:5.1":"Deseti madhuram dhammam, ","tha-ap533:5.2":"catusaccupasamhitam; ","tha-ap533:5.3":"Nimugge mohapankamhi, ","tha-ap533:5.4":"samuddharati panine. ","tha-ap533:6.1":"Tada ekacaro hutva, ","tha-ap533:6.2":"tapaso himavalayo; ","tha-ap533:6.3":"Nabhasa manusam lokam, ","tha-ap533:6.4":"gacchanto jinamaddasam. ","tha-ap533:7.1":"Upecca santikam tassa, ","tha-ap533:7.2":"assosim dhammadesanam; ","tha-ap533:7.3":"Vannayantassa virassa, ","tha-ap533:7.4":"savakassa mahagunam. ","tha-ap533:8.1":"‘Sankhittena maya vuttam, ","tha-ap533:8.2":"vittharena pakasayam; ","tha-ap533:8.3":"Parisam manca toseti, ","tha-ap533:8.4":"yatha kaccayano ayam. ","tha-ap533:9.1":"Naham evamidhekaccam, ","tha-ap533:9.2":"annam passami savakam; ","tha-ap533:9.3":"Tasmatadagge esaggo, ","tha-ap533:9.4":"evam dharetha bhikkhavo’. ","tha-ap533:10.1":"Tadaham vimhito hutva, ","tha-ap533:10.2":"sutva vakyam manoramam; ","tha-ap533:10.3":"Himavantam gamitvana, ","tha-ap533:10.4":"ahitva pupphasancayam. ","tha-ap533:11.1":"Pujetva lokasaranam, ","tha-ap533:11.2":"tam thanamabhipatthayim; ","tha-ap533:11.3":"Tada mamasayam natva, ","tha-ap533:11.4":"byakasi sa rananjaho. ","tha-ap533:12.1":"‘Passathetam isivaram, ","tha-ap533:12.2":"niddhantakanakattacam; ","tha-ap533:12.3":"Uddhaggalomam pinamsam, ","tha-ap533:12.4":"acalam panjalim thitam. ","tha-ap533:13.1":"Hasam supunnanayanam, ","tha-ap533:13.2":"buddhavannagatasayam; ","tha-ap533:13.3":"Dhammajam uggahadayam, ","tha-ap533:13.4":"amatasittasannibham’. ","tha-ap533:14.1":"Kaccanassa gunam sutva, ","tha-ap533:14.2":"tam thanam patthayam thito; ","tha-ap533:14.3":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","tha-ap533:14.4":"gotamassa mahamune. ","tha-ap533:15.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap533:15.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap533:15.3":"Kaccano nama namena, ","tha-ap533:15.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap533:16.1":"Bahussuto mahanani, ","tha-ap533:16.2":"adhippayavidu mune; ","tha-ap533:16.3":"Papunissati tam thanam, ","tha-ap533:16.4":"yathayam byakato maya. ","tha-ap533:17.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap533:17.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap533:17.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap533:17.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap533:18.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap533:18.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap533:18.3":"Annam gatim na gacchami, ","tha-ap533:18.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap533:19.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap533:19.2":"khattiye atha brahmane; ","tha-ap533:19.3":"Nice kule na jayami, ","tha-ap533:19.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap533:20.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap533:20.2":"jato ujjeniyam pure; ","tha-ap533:20.3":"Pajjotassa ca candassa, ","tha-ap533:20.4":"purohitadijadhino. ","tha-ap533:21.1":"Putto tiritivacchassa, ","tha-ap533:21.2":"nipuno vedaparagu; ","tha-ap533:21.3":"Mata ca candima nama, ","tha-ap533:21.4":"kaccanoham varattaco. ","tha-ap533:22.1":"Vimamsanattham buddhassa, ","tha-ap533:22.2":"bhumipalena pesito; ","tha-ap533:22.3":"Disva mokkhapuradvaram, ","tha-ap533:22.4":"nayakam gunasancayam. ","tha-ap533:23.1":"Sutva ca vimalam vakyam, ","tha-ap533:23.2":"gatipankavisosanam; ","tha-ap533:23.3":"Papunim amatam santam, ","tha-ap533:23.4":"sesehi saha sattahi. ","tha-ap533:24.1":"Adhippayavidu jato, ","tha-ap533:24.2":"sugatassa mahamate; ","tha-ap533:24.3":"Thapito etadagge ca, ","tha-ap533:24.4":"susamiddhamanoratho. ","tha-ap533:25.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap533:25.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap533:25.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap533:25.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap533:26.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap533:26.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap533:26.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap533:26.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap533:27.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap533:27.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap533:27.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap533:27.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap533:28.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahakaccayano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap533:29.1":"Mahakaccayanattherassapadanam pathamam. "}